$ System.IO.FileSystemWatcher (class)
@ System.IO.FileSystemWatcher

`System.IO.FileSystemWatcher` monitors directories for changes of files and directories and notifies listeners of such changes.

The class inherits from `System.ComponentModel.Component`.

Possible types of events that can listed for are enumerated in
→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/IO/NotifyFilters[`System.IO.NotifyFilters`]. These events need to be combined with the
enum `→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/IO/WatcherChangeType`.

{ Watching a directory in PowerShell

  gh|.NET-API|/System/IO/FileSystemWatcher/watch-directory.ps1||

}

sa:

  The WinAPI functions `ReadDirectoryChangesW` and `ReadDirectoryChangesExW`.

  Oracle's → development/databases/Oracle/objects/file/watchers object.
